batch_size = 32
features = ['Open','High','Low','Close','Volume']
n_features = len(features)
TRAIN_SIZE = int(len(df)*0.7)

scaler = StandardScaler()

scaled = scaler.transform(df[features].values)

    length = window_size,
    stride=1,
    sampling_rate=1,
    batch_size= batch_size,
    shuffle=False,
    start_index=0,
    end_index=None,
)

LSTM 모델

In [129]:
# 2개 층의 LSTM으로 인코더 만듬
inputs = Input( shape=(window_size, n_features) )

L1 = LSTM(64, activation='relu', return_sequences=True )(inputs)
L2 = LSTM(16, activation='relu', return_sequences=False)(L1)

R1 = RepeatVector(window_size)(L2)#input을 window_size만큼 복사해줌

L3 = LSTM(16, activation='relu', return_sequences=True)(R1)
L4 = LSTM(64, activation='relu', return_sequences=False)(L3)
output = Dense(n_features)(L4)   
model = Model(inputs, output)
